\f1\b0 \

\f2 Player 1 wins!
\f1 \

\f2 O-O
\f1 \

\f2 XXX
\f1 \

\f2 ---
\f1 \

\f0\b Draw example:
\f1\b0 \

\f2 Game is a draw.
\f1 \

\f2 XOX
\f1 \

\f2 XOO
\f1 \

\f2 OXX\
