\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 If a player in War is dealt more or less than exactly half of the card deck (26 cards), then a warning will display on screen such as this:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf2 Size error in func deal: P1 hand stack is size 27
\f1 \
If a spot on the tic-tac-toe board is already taken by a player's marker and this spot is selected again, the following message will appear:\

\f2 Spot already taken. Please choose another spot.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

